@thepouch.bsky.social we have done our best and mustered within The Big Tree.

I have sealed the Great Door but the kettles are spewing water on it... it holds, for now. We are safe but I know not for how long.

Thank you, Big Tree, Daughter of Galathilion for protecting us.

